heading: Guulrahn Canals Dungeon Guide
content: Guulrahn Canals is an incredible dungeon with Spiders and Zombies and an incredibly fast clear time! is available for Rogues as well. Stock up on your Sigils for this one; you'll run it over and over again for massive hordes of loot! Keep in mind that this , an entirely different dungeon! While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! Reviewed by
